sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Frontend
    participant API as Symfony API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Mercure

    User->>Frontend: Edit a message
    Frontend->>API: PATCH /api/channels/{channelId}/messages/{id}
    API->>API: Validate JWT and author permissions
    API->>DB: Load and update message
    DB-->>API: Message updated
    API->>Mercure: Publish message update
    Mercure-->>Frontend: Updated message event
    API-->>Frontend: 200 OK + updated message
    Frontend-->>User: Refresh edited message
